Well, I'm glad you enjoy my doodles. Technical bits: the eye color is copied and pasted from a photo of a fox. The eye shape is "tareme," which in Chinese cartoons means a character is innocent and shy. She wears her hair in a bun, tied up with a cable tie because she lost her scrunchie. I wasn't sure whether Pepper's lightswitch nose is normally perfectly vertical and perpendicular to the ground or angled a bit, so I guessed. I tried to make her look like Pepper's sister or cousin, with visual cues >implying that she's innocent, shy, and an enormous nerd. If I were to attempt to draw Pepper I would use "tsurime" eyes, indicating confidence, pic related, because she strikes me as generally pretty confident.

On a vaguely related note, I am glad we didn't manage to drive you away completely. And it's always good to know that we've accidentally made someone's life better. This may be 4chan, the Internet Hate Machine, but I have nothing but love for everybody here.
